# 👥 Team Management API Documentation

## 📍 Base URL

```bash
http://localhost:5000/team
```

---

# 🧭 Overview

This module allows students to:

* Create teams
* Invite members
* Accept/reject invitations
* Request to join teams
* Manage join requests
* Leave teams

🔐 Most routes require authentication using **JWT (JSON Web Token)**.

---

# 🔐 Authentication

For protected routes, include:

```http
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
```

---

# 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 1. Create Team

## 🔗 Endpoint

```bash
POST /team/create
```

## 🔐 Auth Required

✅ Yes

## 📥 Request Body

```json
