# 💻 Frontend Examples

## 🧪 Create Team

```js
await fetch("/team/create", {
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({
    name: "Team Alpha",
    type: "pfe"
  })
});
```

---

## 🧪 Invite Student

```js
await fetch("/team/invite", {
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`,
    "Content-Type": "application/json"
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({ student_id: 5 })
});
```

---

## 🧪 Accept Invitation

```js
await fetch("/team/accept-invitation", {
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`,
    "Content-Type": "application/json"
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({ invitation_id: 10 })
});
```

