# ⚠️ Important Notes

## 🔴 Authentication

* All protected routes require JWT
* Missing/invalid token → `401 Unauthorized`

---

## 🔴 Authorization (Backend Recommendations)

* Only team owner can accept/reject join requests
* Only invited user can accept invitation
* Only sender can cancel invitation

---

## 🔴 Team Rules (Suggested)

* A student can belong to only one team
* Limit team size (e.g. 3–5 members)
* Restrict team creation to PFE students (optional)

---

# 🚀 Recommended Improvements

* Add `/team/my-team` (get current user team)
* Add `/team/members`
* Add notifications system (invites/requests)
* Add role/middleware checks (e.g. PFE eligibility)

